1
00:00:14,675 --> 00:00:20,113
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,948 --> 00:00:28,855
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,923 --> 00:00:34,293
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,361 --> 00:00:38,422
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,667 --> 00:00:44,570
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,306 --> 00:00:52,212
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,614 --> 00:00:57,106
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,184 --> 00:01:04,147
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,225 --> 00:01:11,290
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,365 --> 00:01:18,032
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:28,007
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:33,765 --> 00:01:38,566
Gentle Fist: 8 Trigrams 64 Palms!

13
00:01:39,871 --> 00:01:40,701
<i>Uh oh!</i>

14
00:01:44,009 --> 00:01:45,203
8 Trigrams 2 Palms!

15
00:01:50,048 --> 00:01:50,776
4 Palms!

16
00:01:52,651 --> 00:01:53,481
8 Palms!

17
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:55,809
16 Palms!

18
00:01:56,989 --> 00:01:57,887
32 Palms!

19
00:02:00,492 --> 00:02:01,618
64 Palms!

20
00:02:23,849 --> 00:02:25,578
<i>What's going on?!</i>

21
00:02:41,033 --> 00:02:43,001
<i>A golden body surface...?

22
00:03:08,093 --> 00:03:11,187
<i>It's the same material as the weapon</i>
<i>he spit out of his mouth earlier...</i>

23
00:03:13,465 --> 00:03:15,092
That was close.

24
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,793
I hear that if you're hit straight on
with Gentle Fist,

25
00:03:17,869 --> 00:03:19,302
your Chakra Network gets damaged

26
00:03:19,371 --> 00:03:21,362
and you become unable
to build up Chakra...

27
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,200
That was close.

28
00:03:25,644 --> 00:03:26,975
Are you a monster?

29
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,207
It seems to come
not just from your mouth.

30
00:03:32,184 --> 00:03:34,152
Gum Style Spider Thread...

31
00:03:34,219 --> 00:03:37,655
is a metal that hardens
the instant it leaves my body.

32
00:03:38,023 --> 00:03:40,457
Moreover, it doesn't let Chakra through.

33
00:03:41,193 --> 00:03:46,290
And... it can be secreted
not just from my mouth,

34
00:03:46,364 --> 00:03:49,458
but also from the sweat glands
throughout my body.

35
00:03:59,077 --> 00:04:03,980
<i>Attacks on Chakra points won't work.</i>
<i>Now it makes sense...</i>

36
00:04:12,390 --> 00:04:14,449
<i>The Spider Web Net won't work.</i>

37
00:04:14,726 --> 00:04:16,387
<i>And there'll be no close range</i>
<i>combat fighting</i>

38
00:04:16,461 --> 00:04:18,053
<i>against a Gentle Fist opponent.</i>

39
00:04:18,463 --> 00:04:19,589
<i>In other words,</i>

40
00:04:19,664 --> 00:04:22,690
<i>I just have to attack the blind side</i>
<i>from long distance.</i>

41
00:05:12,784 --> 00:05:16,743
<i>There'll be no sound...</i>
<i>It'll be in a flash.</i>

42
00:05:24,029 --> 00:05:26,054
<i>The game's over.</i>

43
00:05:30,335 --> 00:05:31,267
<i>The Kunai Knife is a fake!</i>

44
00:05:38,143 --> 00:05:39,041
<i>What?!</i>

45
00:05:39,945 --> 00:05:41,207
8 Trigrams Palm...

46
00:05:42,047 --> 00:05:42,945
Rotation!

47
00:05:52,791 --> 00:05:55,191
<i>Wha-?! What is that?!</i>

48
00:06:04,336 --> 00:06:08,102
<i>Does he...have eyes behind him?!</i>

49
00:06:09,541 --> 00:06:11,907
<i>And the defense just now...</i>

50
00:06:12,577 --> 00:06:15,375
<i>He repelled physical attacks</i>
<i>with Chakra?!</i>

51
00:06:17,215 --> 00:06:23,313
<i>360 Degrees of Vision.</i>
<i>The Byakugan's Blind Spot!</i>

52
00:06:34,332 --> 00:06:36,698
<i>If we're not prepared for</i>
<i>"one person, one kill,"</i>

53
00:06:36,768 --> 00:06:38,292
<i>then it's not going to work out...</i>

54
00:06:39,638 --> 00:06:41,162
<i>That's what you said earlier.</i>

55
00:06:42,641 --> 00:06:46,907
<i>Hurry up and go!</i>
<i>I'll catch up with you all!</i>

56
00:06:52,150 --> 00:06:54,675
<i>We have to be prepared for</i>
<i>"one person, one kill."</i>

57
00:06:55,954 --> 00:06:57,421
<i>Naruto...</i>

58
00:06:58,189 --> 00:07:01,022
<i>You've got better eyes than me.</i>

59
00:07:03,962 --> 00:07:04,951
<i>Neji...</i>

60
00:07:05,764 --> 00:07:07,823
<i>Catch up with us, no matter what!</i>

61
00:07:21,346 --> 00:07:22,973
<i>Can he see me?!</i>

62
00:07:25,083 --> 00:07:27,017
<i>What the heck is he?!</i>

63
00:07:29,321 --> 00:07:31,289
I know you're there.

64
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:33,422
Come out.

65
00:07:34,693 --> 00:07:35,921
<i>Those eyes...</i>

66
00:07:36,494 --> 00:07:39,691
<i>It seems they can do more</i>
<i>than just see through the Chakra flow...</i>

67
00:07:40,832 --> 00:07:43,562
<i>So I see there was</i>
<i>an extraordinary Visual Jutsu user.</i>

68
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:47,138
<i>A long range battle</i>
<i>is unfavorable...</i>

69
00:07:48,039 --> 00:07:50,906
<i>I must bring this to</i>
<i>close combat by all means.</i>

70
00:07:51,776 --> 00:07:52,834
<i>Very well.</i>

71
00:07:57,716 --> 00:08:03,211
I'll acknowledge that this game has
a somewhat high level of difficulty!

72
00:08:04,556 --> 00:08:06,751
I too shall go for it seriously...

73
00:08:10,662 --> 00:08:13,130
<i>It's like he's a totally different person</i>
<i>from before...</i>

74
00:08:13,832 --> 00:08:15,925
<i>His Chakra activity is overwhelming.</i>

75
00:08:17,602 --> 00:08:19,900
<i>And those markings...</i>

76
00:08:27,245 --> 00:08:29,145
<i>His move earlier...</i>

77
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:31,305
<i>He dodged an attack aimed</i>
<i>from behind</i>

78
00:08:31,383 --> 00:08:33,749
<i>and was able to see me hiding</i>
<i>in the shadows.</i>

79
00:08:35,453 --> 00:08:36,943
<i>In other words,</i>

80
00:08:37,021 --> 00:08:40,013
<i>he has a combined wide range</i>
<i>of sight and X ray vision.</i>

81
00:08:41,025 --> 00:08:43,493
<i>And what's more, that Jutsu...</i>

82
00:08:44,028 --> 00:08:45,290
<i>If so...</i>

83
00:08:50,034 --> 00:08:51,092
Summoning Jutsu!

84
00:08:59,377 --> 00:09:01,709
Your ability...

85
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:05,409
I'll find a way to impeccably assault it.

86
00:09:13,191 --> 00:09:15,921
<i>If he defends</i>
<i>against physical attacks</i>

87
00:09:15,994 --> 00:09:19,361
<i>with a large emission</i>
<i>of Chakra and its Rotation...</i>

88
00:09:19,431 --> 00:09:23,197
<i>all I need to do then is to stop</i>
<i>that Chakra Rotation!</i>

89
00:09:25,603 --> 00:09:26,570
Scatter!

90
00:09:37,582 --> 00:09:38,606
Rotation!

91
00:09:48,259 --> 00:09:49,851
<i>It's starting to stop.</i>

92
00:09:58,403 --> 00:09:59,370
<i>Here!</i>

93
00:10:10,682 --> 00:10:11,706
Die!

94
00:10:24,229 --> 00:10:27,824
<i>He released the Chakra just in time</i>
<i>and repelled the Kunai Knife!</i>

95
00:10:31,569 --> 00:10:32,968
<i>To think he'd stop my Chakra Rotation</i>

96
00:10:33,037 --> 00:10:35,028
<i>by binding it with Chakra threads...</i>

97
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,302
<i>These things...</i>

98
00:10:38,476 --> 00:10:39,841
<i>I just have to cut them for now.</i>

99
00:10:42,614 --> 00:10:44,241
<i>If the Rotation won't do,</i>

100
00:10:44,315 --> 00:10:46,146
<i>then I just have to dodge</i>
<i>each and every one.</i>

101
00:10:48,019 --> 00:10:50,852
<i>This guy uses</i>
<i>close range Taijutsu style combat.</i>

102
00:10:51,122 --> 00:10:53,454
<i>There will be no problem</i>
<i>if I fight him from afar.</i>

103
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:59,618
<i>In that way...</i>
<i>I'll have a good long look at your ability.</i>

104
00:11:29,227 --> 00:11:32,094
8 Trigrams, 64 Palms!

105
00:11:40,204 --> 00:11:41,296
<i>What a number!</i>

106
00:12:02,527 --> 00:12:05,223
<i>Hm?! His stance changed?!</i>

107
00:12:06,331 --> 00:12:07,628
8 Trigrams.

108
00:12:08,333 --> 00:12:09,823
128 Palms!

109
00:12:22,547 --> 00:12:25,482
<i>He's fast!</i>
<i>The number of strikes has doubled...!</i>

110
00:12:26,484 --> 00:12:29,214
<i>If I get nailed by that straight on,</i>
<i>it'll be the end for me.</i>

111
00:12:30,154 --> 00:12:32,145
<i>If that's the case on his end,</i>

112
00:12:32,223 --> 00:12:34,418
<i>then it'll be a battle of numbers</i>
<i>on this end, too!</i>

113
00:12:52,176 --> 00:12:55,339
<i>The number's too great!</i>
<i>I won't have enough time!</i>

114
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:03,851
<i>The Rotation's no good,</i>
<i>just as I thought...</i>

115
00:13:17,568 --> 00:13:20,731
<i>It seems he has 360 degree vision.</i>

116
00:13:21,272 --> 00:13:23,433
<i>And it seems he deals</i>
<i>with enemy attacks</i>

117
00:13:23,508 --> 00:13:27,069
<i>by combining his X ray vision ability</i>
<i>for seeing through things</i>

118
00:13:27,145 --> 00:13:30,239
<i>and his telescopic vision ability</i>
<i>for long distance sight.</i>

119
00:13:31,716 --> 00:13:36,415
<i>Furthermore, although</i>
<i>he's got 360 degree vision,</i>

120
00:13:36,487 --> 00:13:38,751
<i>that vision has a formidable extent...</i>

121
00:13:39,857 --> 00:13:44,226
<i>If I were to determine the range</i>
<i>from his reaction before...</i>

122
00:13:44,295 --> 00:13:46,559
<i>he almost unfailingly detected</i>
<i>the Kunai Knives</i>

123
00:13:46,631 --> 00:13:52,194
<i>that entered the approximately</i>
<i>150 foot circumference around him.</i>

124
00:13:54,472 --> 00:13:56,531
<i>But for some reason,</i>

125
00:13:56,607 --> 00:13:58,905
<i>there are Kunai Knives</i>
<i>he can't evade completely.</i>

126
00:14:00,445 --> 00:14:01,742
<i>If so...</i>

127
00:14:08,619 --> 00:14:11,144
8 Trigrams, Sixty...

128
00:14:16,761 --> 00:14:18,194
I see...

129
00:14:31,476 --> 00:14:33,706
<i>This time, there'll be even more.</i>

130
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,754
<i>This time, two will hit...</i>

131
00:15:05,409 --> 00:15:08,810
I've found a way to impeccably
assault your ability!

132
00:15:09,847 --> 00:15:12,213
It seems that defense technique

133
00:15:12,283 --> 00:15:15,684
was something to compensate
for this weak point!

134
00:15:17,121 --> 00:15:22,184
In other words...
Your Visual Jutsu isn't perfect!

135
00:15:32,737 --> 00:15:37,572
Why even bother?!
I've won the game!

136
00:15:47,385 --> 00:15:51,651
Come on. Are you going to
keep at it for naught?

137
00:15:52,423 --> 00:15:57,292
The fate of the small fry character in an
easy game is to be destroyed right away!

138
00:16:00,464 --> 00:16:02,295
You can't beat me!

139
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:11,835
- I-I'm not done yet.
- Lee...

140
00:16:12,243 --> 00:16:15,110
You never give up do you?

141
00:16:15,179 --> 00:16:20,310
No way you can beat him.
He's a genius unlike you.

142
00:16:21,652 --> 00:16:24,355
Genius? What is genius anyway!

143
00:16:24,355 --> 00:16:28,291
Even without any talent,
I'll surpass "genius" by working hard.

144
00:16:28,459 --> 00:16:30,051
It's no use, Lee.

145
00:16:31,696 --> 00:16:35,792
No matter how hard you work,
you cannot beat me.

146
00:16:36,534 --> 00:16:38,331
It's already decided.

147
00:16:38,936 --> 00:16:40,198
Lady Hinata...

148
00:16:40,271 --> 00:16:43,399
You're the sheltered little baby
of the main branch.

149
00:16:43,474 --> 00:16:46,034
A person can never change.

150
00:16:48,446 --> 00:16:49,913
And then, this match...

151
00:16:50,248 --> 00:16:54,708
Your destiny was decided at the point
when I became your opponent.

152
00:16:57,688 --> 00:17:01,180
You don't know until you try!

153
00:17:05,529 --> 00:17:07,497
<i>This is the end...</i>

154
00:17:36,294 --> 00:17:37,056
<i>Gentle Fist!</i>

155
00:17:47,038 --> 00:17:51,441
<i>Small fry character one...</i>
<i>Destruction completed.</i>

156
00:18:13,464 --> 00:18:17,366
<i>Well, for a crummy game,</i>
<i>I was entertained...</i>

157
00:19:05,016 --> 00:19:09,476
<i>Heh... I missed the fatal spots, huh?</i>

158
00:19:10,087 --> 00:19:15,115
<i>And he wouldn't easily die from</i>
<i>Kunai Knives from 150 feet away, eh?</i>

159
00:19:17,962 --> 00:19:21,796
<i>I see...</i>
<i>He's still going to entertain me, huh?</i>

160
00:19:23,534 --> 00:19:25,297
<i>This is thanks for that.</i>

161
00:19:39,250 --> 00:19:42,219
Seriously, that fat Jirobo
can't be helped,

162
00:19:42,286 --> 00:19:44,777
but what's that clod Kidomaru
doing anyway...?

163
00:19:45,022 --> 00:19:46,455
That lowlife!

164
00:19:47,191 --> 00:19:50,251
He's got the habit of playing games.

165
00:19:50,327 --> 00:19:53,023
Maybe he's found someone
to entertain him?

166
00:19:53,330 --> 00:19:55,230
When that idiot plays too much,

167
00:19:55,299 --> 00:19:58,894
he becomes hyper
and easily gets into that state...

168
00:20:02,073 --> 00:20:05,565
But still...
Once he gets to the second state...

169
00:20:05,643 --> 00:20:07,543
it's instant death for the opponent.

170
00:20:37,174 --> 00:20:48,881
<i>Maximum destructive power...</i>
<i>with 100% accuracy!</i>

171
00:20:59,964 --> 00:21:01,591
<i>Die!</i>

172
00:21:11,743 --> 00:21:14,143
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

173
00:21:14,212 --> 00:21:17,238
<i>And you smiled</i>

174
00:21:17,482 --> 00:21:19,780
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

175
00:21:19,851 --> 00:21:22,581
<i>In my own words</i>

176
00:21:22,654 --> 00:21:28,217
<i>Would you think it was</i>
<i>a bother if I approached you?</i>

177
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:33,759
<i>Despite my doubts,</i>
<i>I worked up my courage</i>

178
00:21:34,032 --> 00:21:39,436
<i>My clumsy attempts with words</i>

179
00:21:39,638 --> 00:21:45,167
<i>You listened without turning away</i>

180
00:21:46,144 --> 00:21:51,343
<i>No wonder I get carried away by you</i>

181
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:58,417
<i>But you don't feel anything for me, do you?</i>

182
00:21:58,924 --> 00:22:01,620
<i>I feel so sad</i>

183
00:22:01,693 --> 00:22:02,591
<i>But...</i>

184
00:22:02,661 --> 00:22:05,061
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

185
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:08,099
<i>And you smiled</i>

186
00:22:08,233 --> 00:22:10,827
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

187
00:22:10,902 --> 00:22:13,894
<i>In my own words</i>

188
00:22:14,072 --> 00:22:16,404
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

189
00:22:16,475 --> 00:22:19,603
<i>And you smiled</i>

190
00:22:19,678 --> 00:22:22,146
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

191
00:22:22,214 --> 00:22:25,115
<i>In my own words</i>

192
00:22:25,317 --> 00:22:29,754
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

193
00:22:38,196 --> 00:22:39,891
He doesn't carry out wasteful attacks.

194
00:22:39,965 --> 00:22:42,957
And he accurately reads
information from the results.

195
00:22:43,035 --> 00:22:47,404
No mistake, this guy's the strongest
of all I've fought up until now!

196
00:22:47,873 --> 00:22:50,273
I probably won't be able
to evade the next attack.

197
00:22:50,876 --> 00:22:54,334
I've had enough.
I can't dodge it anyway.

198
00:22:54,679 --> 00:22:59,241
Since the secret of my eyes
has been discovered, I won't run or hide!

199
00:22:59,951 --> 00:23:02,419
Next episode: "Losing is Not an Option!"
